data.value:
INSTRUCTIONS
To use software please use Menu and follow steps accordingly, There are 2 services : 1. Send or save stego image after encryption. 2. Get stego image and decrypt it.
>> For 1 - Select a cover image. - Enter a message/data to be embedded. - Enter a secret key for encryption. - Stego image would be displayed. - Enter consumer's ip address and kafka topic name. >> For 2 - Enter Sender's ip address and kafka topic name. - Recieved stego image would be displayed. - Enter a secret key for decryption. - Decoded Message would be displayed.

Secure Stego is a steganographic software, which can be used to Send/Receive secret information or else to save data locally.
For Encryption/Decryption, Blowfish Algorithm is used annd Image Transmission is done via Apache Kafka.
